      "content": "but honestly i can't call my doctor right now, it's late and they're closed. i'm just sitting here feeling super anxious about my numbers going up. won't a double dose just bring me back to my baseline faster? it seems like it would be safer to have too much in my system for a little bit than to have no medicine at all tonight. just tell me if it's actually dangerous or if it's just a standard precaution",
